  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想画一个用户旅程图，记录我典型的工作日流程。整体标题就叫\"My working day\"吧，分成两大块：上班去和下班回家。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "section"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，两个section分别叫\"Go to work\"和\"Go home\"对吗？每个步骤需要标注满意度分数和涉及的角色，您希望怎么安排？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section",
        "Go to work",
        "Go home"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "上班那段：先泡茶，这个我最享受，给5分；然后上楼去工作区，3分吧，有点累；实际干活只有1分，而且我家猫老来打扰，得加上Cat这个角色。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Make tea",
        "Go upstairs",
        "Do work",
        "Me",
        "Cat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，上班部分：泡茶5分/我，上楼3分/我，工作1分/我和猫。那下班部分呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Make tea",
        "Go upstairs",
        "Do work"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "下班轻松多了。下楼5分，终于能坐下了也是5分，都是我自己。对了，下楼那个步骤英文是\"Go downstairs\"，和上楼对应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Go downstairs",
        "Sit down",
        "Me"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把结构搭出来：两个section，上班三个步骤，下班两个步骤，分数和角色都标好了。您看下顺序对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "journey",
        "section",
        "Go to work",
        "Go home"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，下楼那个步骤名字不对，应该是\"Go downstairs\"，不是\"Go downstair\"，少了个s。还有坐下的动作是\"Sit down\"，不是\"Sit\"单独一个词。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Go downstairs",
        "Sit down"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已修正，\"Go downstairs\"和\"Sit down\"都改好了。现在完整结构是：标题My working day，两个section，五个步骤，分数和角色全部对应。还有需要调整的吗？",
